particular to resolve the Sudanese problem peacefully. She also 
briefed President Issaias on the U.S. Government's readiness to 
cooperate with IGADD member countries in bringing lasting peace 
to the region. President Issaias noted that the appointment of 
a special envoy to Sudan by the U.S. Government clearly showed 
their desire to solve the problem. [passage omitted] 

